text: Boischampré is a commune in the Orne department in northwestern France. It was formed in 2015 by the merger of the former communes Saint-Christophe-le- Jajolet, Marcei, Saint-Loyer-des-Champs and Vrigny. ==See also== *Communes of the Orne department ==References== Category:Communes of Orne
title: Boischampré
